en_460559_0	Minister of Lands and Parliamentary Reforms Gayantha Karunatilake has said necessary initiatives have been taken for the resolution of land issues of the people of the country.
en_460559_1	He said that the Land Reforms Commission has been set up and the staff increased to undertake this work.
en_460559_2	The Minister expressed these views after opening a sub office of the Land Reforms Commission in the Galle District.
en_460559_3	People who are encountering lands issued in the Elpitiya, Karandeniya, Welivitiya, Divithura, Benthota and Niyagama Divisional Secretariat Divisions will benefit by this effort.
en_460559_4	The Minister handed over deeds to 50 families that did not have land entitlements.
